    "faqtext": "此處彙整了常見問題。如仍有疑問，請至 GitHub 儲存庫提交回饋。",
    "@faqtext": {
        "description": "Here you find answers to some of the most frequent questions. If you have any other questions, feel free to open an issue on the github repository."
    },
    "faq_q1": "為什麼某些功能尚未提供？",
    "@faq_q1": {
        "description": "The feature/function X is missing. When will it be implemented?"
    },
    "faq_a1": "本應用以簡潔與可長期維護為設計原則，避免引入過多可能影響使用體驗的功能。如你認為缺少關鍵功能，歡迎回報問題或提交合併請求。",
    "@faq_a1": {
        "description": "The app is maintained in our free time and we try to keep the app sleek and simple. We believe that adding to many features making the app less usable. If you believe that we are missing a key feature, feel free to open an issue or a merge request."
    },
    "faq_q2": "可以再次查看引導畫面嗎？",
    "@faq_q2": {
        "description": "Can I see once again the intro/onboarding screen?"
    },
    "faq_a2": "可以！點擊下方按鈕即可重新進入。",
    "@faq_a2": {
        "description": "Yes for sure! Simple press the icon below."
    },
    "faq_a2_widget": "返回引導畫面",
    "@faq_a2_widget": {
        "description": "Return to onboarding screen"
    },
    "faq_q3": "應用程式圖示代表什麼？",
    "@faq_q3": {
        "description": "What is the app icon showing?"
    },
    "faq_a3": "圖示為一隻坐姿狼的形象，尾部與字母「t」「r」結合。",
    "@faq_a3": {
        "description": "It shows a wolf sitting an the letter 'r' and its tail is partially hidden by the letter 't'."
    },
    "faq_q4": "可以設定較低的目標體重嗎？",
    "@faq_q4": {
        "description": "Can I enter a target weight below 50kg / 110 lb / 7.9 st?"
    },
    "faq_a4": "可以，需提供身高資訊。\n\n為支持健康風險防控，系統不允許設定低於安全閾值的目標體重。輸入身高後，系統將依 BMI 18.5 自動計算最低可設定的目標體重。",
    "@faq_a4": {
        "description": "Yes, by providing your height.\nAnorexia is a serious disease that is increasingly becoming a problem for society as a whole, partly due to the many negative examples on social media. To support prevention efforts, we do not allow target weights below 50 kg / 110 lb / 7.9 st. Entering your height allows us to calculate a minimum target weight corresponding to a BMI of 18.5."
    },
    "target_weight_warning": "為支持健康風險防控，不允許設定低於 50 kg 或 BMI < 18.5 的目標體重。",
    "@target_weight_warning": {
        "description": "Anorexia is a serious disease that is increasingly becoming a problem for society as a whole, partly due to the many negative examples on social media. To support prevention efforts, we do not allow target weights below  50 kg / 110 lb / 7.9 st and BMIs below 18.5."
    },
